# Leacme.Glinter

**Leacme Glinter** is a cross-platform application that is currently targeted for mobile devices. It is build using the [Godot Engine](https://github.com/godotengine/godot).

This application features the ability to flash the device screen at the specified color and rate.

![][image_screenshot]
![index](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6654513/71702160-1557c880-2d8b-11ea-9a37-69d065a4b901.png)

## Application Compiling

The application can be compiled into the platform-specific executable with the Godot Engine via the following [instructions](https://docs.godotengine.org/en/latest/getting_started/workflow/export/index.html). Make sure to run `nuget restore` to fetch dependencies specified in the .csproj file prior to building with Godot.

## Application Usage

Use the controls at the top to choose the flash color and rate.
